        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "It can easily implement by adding 3 lines of code in  Zend_Translate_Adapter_Array::_loadTranslationData()\n\n{code}\n\nif(!is_array($data)){\n    $data = include($data); \n}\n{code}\n\n\nThen the array file should look like :\n{code}\n<?php\nreturn array(\n    'user_id'  => 'Id',\n    'username' => 'Non utilisateur',\n    'password' => 'Mot de passe',\n    'email'    => 'Email',\n    'firstname'=> 'Pr\u00e9nom',\n    'lastname' => 'Nom',\n    'created'  => 'Cr\u00e9e le',\n    'modified' => 'Modifi\u00e9 le'\n);\n{code}\n\n"
        },
